    <section id="intro">
      <span class="hero-tag">Independent Review · Updated July 2026</span>
      <h1>FastBots.ai Review: An Independent, Research-Based Analysis</h1>

      <p><strong>FastBots.ai</strong> is a no-code AI chatbot builder that lets businesses create custom chatbots trained on their own content — website pages, documents, and other data sources — and deploy them across multiple channels including website widgets, WhatsApp, Instagram, Facebook Messenger, Telegram, Slack, and email. Based on official documentation, a captured product snapshot, and independent third-party sources, our assessment is this: FastBots.ai offers a straightforward, multi-channel chatbot platform with strong training ingestion and a generous free tier, but advanced features require higher-tier plans and several important capabilities can only be verified through hands-on testing.</p>

      <div class="verdict-box">
        <p><strong>Best for:</strong> small-to-medium businesses, agencies needing white-label solutions, e-commerce stores, SaaS companies, and non-technical business owners who want a chatbot live in under five minutes without coding.</p>
        <p><strong>Not ideal for:</strong> organisations requiring on-premises deployment, teams that need a drag-and-drop conversation flow builder, or enterprises with HIPAA-specific compliance requirements that have not been confirmed.</p>
      </div>

      <h3>What Is FastBots.ai, and Who Is It For?</h3>
      <p>FastBots.ai is a cloud-based SaaS platform founded in 2022 by CEO Jason West and based in the United Kingdom. It allows users to train an AI chatbot on their own content — website URLs, sitemaps, PDFs, DOCX files, CSV spreadsheets, Google Sheets, and even YouTube videos — and then embed that chatbot on their website via a JavaScript snippet, or connect it to messaging platforms. The platform supports 12+ large language models from OpenAI, Anthropic, and Google, giving users control over which underlying AI powers their chatbot.</p>
      <p>The target market spans solo entrepreneurs, small-to-medium businesses, e-commerce stores, SaaS companies, agencies, educational institutions, and enterprises. Industry-specific landing pages exist for dentists, schools, hotels and B&Bs, e-commerce stores, SaaS companies, and gyms. Notable listed customers include Royal Caribbean, Holiday Inn, the University of Miami, the University of Arizona, Syngenta, Rentokil Initial, Wiley, Design Bundles, and Big Cat Rescue.</p>

      <h3>Author Background &amp; Review Methodology</h3>
      <div class="methodology">
        <p><strong>Who wrote this:</strong> This review was prepared by an editorial research team that evaluates online business tools, AI products, and digital-education platforms with attention to factual accuracy and separation of verified information from vendor claims.</p>
        <p><strong>How this review was built:</strong> We did not purchase or personally test FastBots.ai. This article is based on independent desk research: a 35-page PDF FireShot capture of the official FastBots.ai homepage (captured July 4, 2026), cross-referenced against the live website, plus official documentation pages (About, Industries, Integrations, Use Cases), the public FAQ, and five independent third-party sources (AI Tools Mentor, G2, TechnologyChecker, AI Chat Review, and the FastBots Blog). Where a capability could not be verified without hands-on testing — including response quality, hallucination resistance, and auto retraining reliability — we state that explicitly rather than speculating.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div class="cta-card">
      <h3>Build your first AI chatbot — free, no credit card required</h3>
      <p>FastBots.ai lets you create a custom AI chatbot trained on your own content in minutes. Deploy it on your website, WhatsApp, Instagram, Messenger, and more — all from one dashboard. Start with the free plan and upgrade when you need more.</p>
      <p><a href="https://fastbots.ai/?via=jarmo" class="cta-btn" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer sponsored">Try FastBots.ai Free →</a></p>
      <p style="font-size:.82rem; color:var(--ink-light); margin:0;">If you choose to join FastBots.ai through this link, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.</p>
    </div>

    <section id="overview">
      <h2>FastBots.ai Overview &amp; Pricing</h2>
      <p>FastBots.ai operates on a freemium SaaS model with five paid tiers plus enterprise custom pricing. All pricing below was verified from the official pricing page captured in the PDF snapshot on July 4, 2026. Annual billing saves approximately 17% across all tiers.</p>

      <h3>What's Included</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Website training:</strong> An advanced web crawler that handles JavaScript-heavy sites, firewall-protected content, and sitemaps. The FAQ states: "we can crawl and extract data from almost any website, including javascript sites and those that have active firewalls."</li>
        <li><strong>Document training:</strong> Upload PDF, DOC, DOCX, CSV, XLS, and TXT files. Also supports Google Sheets and YouTube video URLs.</li>
        <li><strong>Three knowledge modes:</strong> Trained content only (strict mode), combined with ChatGPT knowledge, or combined with live internet search. Users control which sources are active per chatbot.</li>
        <li><strong>Multi-channel deployment:</strong> Website embed (JS snippet, iframe, or share link), WhatsApp, Facebook Messenger, Instagram DMs, Telegram, Slack, and email replies (Business+ plan).</li>
        <li><strong>Human handoff:</strong> Live chat takeover when the AI cannot answer. Available on Business plan and above with configurable availability hours.</li>
        <li><strong>Auto retraining:</strong> Scheduled revisiting of website sources (daily, weekly, or monthly) to keep the chatbot current. Available on Business plan and above.</li>
        <li><strong>Lead capture:</strong> Built-in collection of contact details during conversations, emailed to configured addresses and exportable.</li>
        <li><strong>White-label:</strong> Full platform rebranding with custom domain and client login. Available on Reseller plan ($399/month) or via add-ons.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Pricing Tiers</h3>
      <div class="table-scroll">
