      <h2>Features &amp; Performance</h2>

      <h3>Core Mechanic: How FastBots.ai Works</h3>
      <p>The platform follows a three-step process: Import Data (upload website URLs, documents, or other sources), Customise Bot (set welcome message, chat icon, colour scheme, and tone via custom prompts), and Start Using (embed on website or connect to messaging channels). The chatbot then answers visitor questions based on the trained content.</p>

