    <section id="faq">
      <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <details>
        <summary>What is FastBots.ai?</summary>
        <p>FastBots.ai is a no-code AI chatbot builder that lets businesses create custom chatbots trained on their own content — website pages, documents, PDFs, and other data sources. Chatbots can be deployed on a website widget, WhatsApp, Instagram, Facebook Messenger, Telegram, Slack, and email, all from a single trained model.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Is FastBots.ai free?</summary>
        <p>Yes, there is a free plan with 1 chatbot and 50 message credits per month, no credit card required. It is sufficient for testing but limited — training data is cleared after 14 days of inactivity. Paid plans start at $39/month for the Essential tier.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>How does the message credit system work?</summary>
        <p>Each chatbot response consumes message credits. Standard models (GPT-4o Mini, Gemini 2.5 Flash, Claude 3.5 Haiku) use 1 credit per response. Advanced models use more: GPT-4o and GPT-5 use 5 credits; Claude 4.5 Sonnet uses 10 credits. The free plan includes 50 credits per month; paid plans range from 2,000 to 30,000 credits per month. Additional credits can be purchased as add-ons.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can I use my own domain for the chatbot?</summary>
        <p>Yes. A custom domain for chatbot embeds and share links is available as a $49/month add-on on any plan, or is included natively in the Reseller plan ($399/month).</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Does FastBots.ai support multiple languages?</summary>
        <p>The platform supports approximately 95 languages. Visitors can chat in their preferred language, and the chatbot responds in the same language. Automated translation ensures conversations appear in the user's chosen language. Chat translation for reviewing transcripts is available on the Business plan and above.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can a human take over from the chatbot?</summary>
        <p>Yes. The Live Chat / human handover feature (Business plan and above) lets the chatbot offer a transfer to a human agent when it cannot answer. The team member receives the full conversation transcript and can continue in real time. Availability hours can be configured.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>Can I white-label FastBots.ai for my clients?</summary>
        <p>Yes. The Reseller plan ($399/month) provides a fully branded version of the platform with custom domain, custom "Powered by" text, and client login portals for up to 5 different brands. Lower plans can remove the "Powered by FastBots" branding as a $29/month add-on.</p>
      </details>
      <details>
        <summary>How is FastBots.ai different from ChatGPT?</summary>
        <p>ChatGPT is a general-purpose conversational AI. FastBots.ai lets you train a chatbot specifically on your own content — your website, documents, FAQs, and policies — so it answers based on your information rather than general knowledge. You control whether the chatbot can also draw on ChatGPT's general knowledge or live web search.</p>
      </details>
